Windmi Controller - Debian Packaging Notes
==========================================

The binary is installed as /usr/bin/windmi-control.

Configuration is at /etc/windmi-controller.conf.

Usage:
  sudo windmi-control --web 8080 --ip 192.168.123.10 --port 8899

For demo/testing without hardware:
  sudo windmi-control --demo --web 8080

See 'windmi-control --help' for all options.
